Sophie
shifted
her
position
so
they
were
sitting
side
by
side.
Langdon
suddenly
felt
like
they
were
two
kids
huddled
over
a
Christmas
present.
In
contrast
to
the
warm
colors
of
the
rosewood
box,
the
inlaid
rose
had
been
crafted
of
a
pale
wood,
probably
ash,
which
shone
clearly
in
the
dim
light.
The
Rose.
Entire
armies
and
religions
had
been
built
on
this
symbol,
as
had
secret
societies.
The
Rosicrucians.
The
Knights
of
the
Rosy
Cross.
"Go
